title: This made me laugh so hard
body:
So I was playing some J4 jungle in norms when i ran into some lee sin who got pretty damn fed. Late game though, we were making a pretty strong comeback. I guess it didn't matter though, cause we lost anyways, but at one point after i unleashed my full combo on lee he typed in chat "Jarvan jungle is OP".


....


For fucks sake

replies.body:
lmfao.
he barely works in the jungle now, i think?
He can stomp lower elo, but if any decent jungler knows what they're doing, they can easily invade Jarvan early on (since his clear is so terrible) and he's basically fucked for the rest of the game.
